            "id": 6097674,
            "title": "盤中速報 - Crowdstrike控股(CRWD-US)大跌5.02%，報429美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Crowdstrike控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRWD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRWD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRWD-US</a>)截至台北時間07日23:48股價下跌22.69美元，報429.00美元，跌幅5.02%，成交量2,418,465（股），盤中最高價451.69美元、最低價429.00美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.68%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.1%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.37%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.5%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Crowdstrike控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRWD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRWD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRWD-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-2.47%</li> <li>近 1 月：-12.14%</li> <li>近 3 月：+1.91%</li> <li>近 6 月：+7.41%</li> <li>今年以來：+32.01%</li></ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6097674",
